fields.System.Title: Establishing Strategy
fields.System.Description: Once the business out come is defined, establish the strategy to execute the migrate the application.

fields.System.Title: Outlining & Justifying of Business Outcomes
fields.System.Description: This task is to outline on the onsite the justification for migrating application to AKS and specifically what business outcomes are to be achieved as part of the migration.

fields.System.Title: Assessing the Digital Estate
fields.System.Description: This task is to evaluate the larger IT state as part of the migration. Are there other possible aspects of the IT state that can be moved while executing the migration of the containerized application to AKS.

fields.System.Title: Application Assessment
fields.System.Description: This task is to ensure an application assessment is conducted before migration the container application to AKS

fields.System.Title: AKS Adoption Plan
fields.System.Description: This task is define the adoption plan for executing a migration to AKS.

fields.System.Title: Defining and Checking the Prerequisites
fields.System.Description: This task is to define and check for prerequisites required before migration can begin.

fields.System.Title: Other Factors Affecting Deployment
fields.System.Description:
Some special considerations when migration a workload to AKS can be found on the following documentation:
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/aks-migration

fields.System.Title: Establishing AKS Adoption Steps
fields.System.Description: Establish a set up adoption steps based on the application assessment.

fields.System.Title: AKS Setup Guide
fields.System.Description: Setup the AKS cluster deployment guide before migration the containerized application.

fields.System.Title: Best Practices
fields.System.Description: Assess best practices and see which ones are appropriate to adopt as part of the migration.

fields.System.Title: Creating Sandbox
fields.System.Description: Deploy the application into a sandbox environment.

fields.System.Title: Migrate
fields.System.Description: Execute the migration.

fields.System.Title: Migration Strategy
fields.System.Description: Define the migration strategy before executing the migration.

fields.System.Title: Innovate
fields.System.Description: Refactor and innovate as and when appropriate during the migration.

fields.System.Title: Prerequisite Configuration
fields.System.Description: Ensure the the prerequisite configurations for the application are accounted for.

fields.System.Title: Deployment
fields.System.Description: Ensure the appropriate deployment mechanism is adopted. One way to deploy AKS applications is via helm (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/quickstart-helm)

fields.System.Title: Infrastructure Integration
fields.System.Description: This task is to ensure the appropriate infrastructure integrations are accounted for.

fields.System.Title: Application Integration
fields.System.Description: This task is to ensure the application is containerized and ready to be migrated.

fields.System.Title: Governance
fields.System.Description: Evaluate the best practices around security and governance. Apply as and when appropriate (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/concepts-security)

fields.System.Title: Security Policies
fields.System.Description: Evaluate all AKS build-in policies and apply as appropriate (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/policy-samples)

fields.System.Title: Automation Needs
fields.System.Description: Automate as much of the process as possible

fields.System.Title: Developer Managing the Cluster
fields.System.Description: Ensure developer management best practices are reviewed and applied where appropriate (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/best-practices#developer-best-practices)

fields.System.Title: Operator Managing the Cluster
fields.System.Description: Look the the provided guides for operating the cluster. (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/best-practices#cluster-operator-best-practices)

fields.System.Title: Organize
fields.System.Description: Ensure the organizational structure is reflected within the AKS deployed resources.

fields.System.Title: Establishing Various Organizational Structures
fields.System.Description: Ensure the appropriate RBAC security posture is adopted as part of the migration.

fields.System.Title: Organizing the Resources Required
fields.System.Description: Ensure the AKS cluster is appropriately scaled.

fields.System.Title: Defining And Following the Best Practices
fields.System.Description: Follow the defined best practices as needed (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/best-practices)

fields.System.Title: Outlining the Business Continuing and Defining the Disaster Recovery
fields.System.Description: task to evaluate and define the HA/DR strategy based on the documentation. (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/operator-best-practices-multi-region)

fields.System.Title: SOW Checklist
fields.System.Description: Ensure the statement of work is fully delivered.

fields.System.Title: Supporting Documents
fields.System.Description: Ensure all supporting documents are delivered.

fields.System.Title: Sign Off Project Delivery
fields.System.Description: Ensure appropriate deliverables are communicated and the sign off is attained before the project is closed out.
